categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: This female Human served as a Jedi Master during the final days of the Galactic Republic.

She examined a young Dass Jennir, and reported that while he had strong concentration, his overall connection to the Force was not. She informed Grand Master Yoda that she believed Jennir would never be a great Jedi, to which he questioned.
